step_data.thought:
I notice that I'm already on the edit page for a product, but it's not the Yoga Mat Pro product I'm looking for - I'm currently on the edit page for 'Phoebe Zipper Sweatshirt' (as shown in the page title and heading). The previous action failed because I tried to click on an element that was from a previous page state but is no longer available.

Looking at the current URL (http://127.0.0.1:7780/admin/catalog/product/edit/id/1130/), I can see I'm editing product ID 1130, but I need to find the Yoga Mat Pro product.

To navigate to the products listing page where I can search for the Yoga Mat Pro, I should first click the 'Back' button which is visible on the current page. This will take me back to the product listing page where I can then search for the Yoga Mat Pro product.

The Back button is element [840] with the text '\ue626 Back'.
